text: Had lunch here on 27 May 2022.. ordered rice with fried chicken, potato balls, and curry vegetable.. added some sambal and the taste is very good.. been awhile since i had nasi padang and its well worth it.. all this for $6.40
One of my favourite here is Squid ink Sotong.
Really nice makcik serving really nice food. Had the masala chicken and wasnâ€™t too spicy for my palate.
